CHAT.comment: nina has been very overexcited and tense from the combination of christmas and her grandparent's visit. her grandparents have been with her for the past week. nina seems to associate her grandparents with the long separation from her mother , since she had been left with them last fall. nina has not been sleeping well at night. she usually wakes up several times during the night. also she has been having a lot of temper tantrums. linda , nina's mother's younger sister arrived last night. this added more excitement to nina's life. linda is with us during this taping session. Nina , linda , and nina's mother are sitting in the living room. nina has just discovered the stocking which santa claus brought to her. we are in the living room.
